# Auto-activate the dotfiles CLI's uv venv when working anywhere in this repo,
# so `python` / `pytest` / `ruff` resolve without `uv run`. The venv lives in
# cli/, not the repo root, hence the explicit path. `layout uv` is defined in
# terminal/direnv/direnvrc. Approve with `direnv allow` after editing.
layout uv cli/.venv
